      <div class="subfield"><strong>$c - ISO country code</strong> <div class="description">Code taken from the International Organization for Standardization's <em>Codes for
                                    the representation of names of countries and their subdivisions - Part 1:
                                    Country codes</em> or <em>Part 2 : Country subdivision codes</em> (ISO
                           3166).
         </div>
