      <div class="subfield"><strong>$2 - Source of local subentity code</strong> <div class="description">Source from which the local code was assigned. Code from: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/country.html">Country Code and Term Source Codes</a></em>.
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Used only when subfield $b is used to indicate a local GAC code.</div>
         </div>
