      <div class="subfield"><strong>$8 - Field link and sequence number</strong> 
        <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                                       Subfields</a></em>.
        </div>
   </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Capitalization</strong> - All codes are recorded in lowercase alphabetic characters.
      </div>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Length</strong> - For two-character codes, the trailing blank (#) is omitted.
      </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="font_small"><em>$c - ISO country code [REDEFINED, 2001]</em><br>Subfield $c was redefined to include both ISO 3166-1 and ISO 3166-2
                     codes.
      </div>
